high_descs: Turn right, move past the coffee table, turn around to face the pencil on the coffee table.
Pick up the pencil on the coffee table.
Turn around, bring the pencil to the table behind the couch.
Put the pencil in the bowl on the table, right of the computer, closest to you.
Pick up the bowl with pencil in it on the table.
Turn right, move around the couch to the right and head to the coffee table.
Put the bowl with pencil on the bottom shelf of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with pencil on the bottom shelf of the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the other side of the coffee table.
Pick up the yellow pencil in front of the white plate.
Turn around and walk to the dining table on the other side of the couch.
Place the pencil inside of the white bowl in front of the sculpture.
Pick up the white bowl from the table.
Turn right and walk back over to the coffee table.
Place the bowl on the bottom shelf of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: To move a pencil and bowl to the coffee table.

high_descs: Go to the coffee table on the side where the pencil is.
Pick up the pencil that is on the shelf on the coffee table.
With the pencil go to the table on the side that is directly behind the couch.
Put the pencil in the bowl that is in front of the statue.
Pick the bowl with the pencil up.
With the bowl with the pencil in hand go to the coffee table on the side of it closest to the white pillow on the couch.
Place the bowl with the pencil in it on the bottom shelf of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Move bowl with pencil to coffee table.
